references.paper_title: Efficient global optimization of expensive black-box functions
references.reason: This paper is foundational to the field of expensive optimization and introduces the well-known efficient global optimization algorithm, which is a core method used in the reviewed paper.

references.paper_title: Scalable test problems for evolutionary multiobjective optimization
references.reason: This paper provides widely used benchmark problems for multiobjective optimization, which are essential for evaluating the performance of the proposed few-shot evolutionary optimization framework.

references.paper_title: Model-agnostic meta-learning for fast adaptation of deep networks
references.reason: This paper introduces a prominent meta-learning algorithm, Model-Agnostic Meta-Learning (MAML), which is crucial for enabling few-shot learning in the proposed framework.

references.paper_title: Evolutionary transfer optimization-a new frontier in evolutionary computation research
references.reason: This survey paper provides a comprehensive overview of evolutionary transfer optimization, which is highly relevant to the few-shot evolutionary optimization approach proposed in the reviewed paper.

references.paper_title: Multiobjective optimization using evolutionary algorithms - a comparative case study
references.reason: This paper offers a foundational comparison of various multiobjective evolutionary algorithms, providing a basis for understanding the context and relative performance of the proposed method.
